{
  "stem": "3605.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because this was the auspices of a formal education, but actually we had underground spiritual activities there that we didn't want the other people to know about.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was in a very kind of fortunate situation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That little apartment that we moved into in that little house was bordering.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The house was in the corner, and then the fence from that house we lived in was bordering with the garden.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So even though the curfew, I could go over that in the evening, and we could work at the-- the vegetables and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the same house downstairs lived another of our members, [NON-ENGLISH], and he used to come and help, too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So this was very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because even if you lived across the street, you couldn't come and cross the street after curfew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he and I could sometimes, when necessary, go over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had to take the water from the pump and pump it in the buckets and-- how's it called that you--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sprinkling cans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were sprinkling the-- the garden, taking the water from the pump.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The majority of our members in my group-- there were three age groups.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- was one that were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 18 to 20-some.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- we were a group that was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] during the war, we were already 14, 15, and 16, and we organized-- in fact, our group organized a group of 12-year-olds during the war, a younger group that we were leading.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, I had-- and a friend of mine had two [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We called them [NON-ENGLISH], those things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and they were called 'dror' and 'la'or,' which means-- dror is freedom, and la'or to light.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
